data.description: Seller offering $4,000 in concessions and IS MOTIVATED!! Beautiful 2 story, 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath chalet within walking distance of Lake Avalon on serene lot with mature trees. Primary bedroom is downstairs, has a sitting area, bench and built in dresser within the walk in closet, and a separate vanity room with sink next to the master bath. There are 2 other bedrooms upstairs both with walk in closets and a bonus room/4th bedroom with tons of closet space and deck overlooking the backyard with a slight view of the lake. Beautiful wood burning fireplace with built-ins on each side.  Open floor plan with plenty of room inside and out for family, entertaining or would make a wonderful Airbnb or vacation home.  Ample parking and 2 car garage. Winter lake views. Refrigerator to convey.
